Package odu.edu.cs.cs350.pne

Class ArffParser

java.lang.Object
odu.edu.cs.cs350.pne.ArffParser
public class ArffParser extends Object
An Arff Parser reads in the text from an arff file and constructs a list of Arff Documents from the data in that text. The resulting Arff Documents hold data that was once associated with Train Documents but then converted into an arff file.
